395  private const byte _Thursday = 8;
396  private const byte _Friday = 16;

400  [XmlElement("monday")] bool Monday { get => WeekDays == null ? false : (WeekDays & _Monday) != 0; set => WeekDays = (byte)(value ? (WeekDays ?? 0) | _Monday : (WeekDays ?? 0) ^ _Monday); }
401  [XmlElement("tuesday")] bool Tuesday { get => WeekDays == null ? false : (WeekDays & _Tuesday) != 0; set => WeekDays = (byte)(value ? (WeekDays ?? 0) | _Tuesday : (WeekDays ?? 0) ^ _Tuesday); }
402  [XmlElement("wednesday")] bool Wednesday { get => WeekDays == null ? false : (WeekDays & _Wednesday) != 0; set => WeekDays = (byte)(value ? (WeekDays ?? 0) | _Wednesday : (WeekDays ?? 0) ^ _Wednesday); }
403  [XmlElement("thursday")] bool Thursday { get => WeekDays == null ? false : (WeekDays & _Thursday) != 0; set => WeekDays = (byte)(value ? (WeekDays ?? 0) | _Thursday : (WeekDays ?? 0) ^ _Thursday); }
404  [XmlElement("friday")] bool Friday { get => WeekDays == null ? false : (WeekDays & _Friday) != 0; set => WeekDays = (byte)(value ? (WeekDays ?? 0) | _Friday : (WeekDays ?? 0) ^ _Friday); }
405  [XmlElement("saturday")] bool Saturday { get => WeekDays == null ? false : (WeekDays & _Saturday) != 0; set => WeekDays = (byte)(value ? (WeekDays ?? 0) | _Saturday : (WeekDays ?? 0) ^ _Saturday); }
406  [XmlElement("sunday")] bool Sunday { get => WeekDays == null ? false : (WeekDays & _Sunday) != 0; set => WeekDays = (byte)(value ? (WeekDays ?? 0) | _Sunday : (WeekDays ?? 0) ^ _Sunday); }
